package work7
  • Class
    Description
    AddRequestCommand
    The class that implements the Command interface receives information about the request to be added and the recipient, the executor of the add request and contains the execute function
    Client
    Main class which creates commands, adds them to the list, and executes them and contains the function main
    Command
    Interface for classes DelRequestCommand, PriChCommand, AddRequestCommand that represent commands to perform an operation on a request, contains a function execute which performs some operation on the request
    DelRequestCommand
    The class that implements the Command interface, receives information about the request to be deleted and the recipient who executed the delete request and contains the execute function
    Invoker
    Class responsible for creating command objects an–≤ call their execution.
    PriChCommand
    The class that implements the Command interface receives information about the request for which it is necessary to change the priority, the new priority and the recipient, the executor of the priority change operations and contains the execute function
    Receiver
    A class that is a request handler and contains 3 functions to operate on request addRequest, removeRequest, changeRequestPriority
